'''葛利澤880'''（GJ 880 / HD 216899 / LHS 533 / Ross 671）<ref name=SIMBAD>[http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?protocol=html&Ident=Gliese+880&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id Gliese 880] {{Wayback|url=http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?protocol=html&Ident=Gliese+880&NbIdent=1&Radius=2&Radius.unit=arcmin&submit=submit+id |date=20140913124833 }} ([[SIMBAD|SIMBAD]])</ref> 位於[[飛馬座|飛馬座]]，是距離[[太陽系|太陽系]]22.4[[光年|光年]]的一個恆星系統<ref name=RECONS>[http://www.chara.gsu.edu/RECONS/TOP100.posted.htm The One Hundred Nearest Star Systems] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120513202710/http://www.chara.gsu.edu/RECONS/TOP100.posted.htm |date=2012-05-13 }} ([[RECONS|RECONS]])</ref>，[[視星等|視星等]]+8.66<ref name=SIMBAD />，裸眼看不見這顆恆星。 

葛利澤880是一顆[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]，[[光譜類型|光譜類型]]為M1.5V<ref name=SIMBAD />，它比太陽小很多，光度僅為[[太陽光度|太陽]]的1.4%，但仍然比鄰近的另一顆紅矮星[[沃夫359|沃夫359]]明亮。它的[[有效溫度|有效溫度]]是3,600[[熱力學溫標|K]]<ref>{{cita publicación
| autor = Morales, J. C.; Ribas, I.; Jordi, C.
| título = The effect of activity on stellar temperatures and radii
| año = 2008
| publicación = [[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]]
| volumen = 478
| número = 2
| id = pp. 507-512 (Tabla consultada en CDS)
| url = http://cdsads.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?2008A%26A...478..507M&db_key=AST&nosetcookie=1
}}</ref>，質量相當於59%[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]，半徑近似於69%[[太陽半徑|太陽半徑]]<ref name=LopezMorales>{{cita publicación
| autor = López-Morales, Mercedes
| título = On the Correlation between the Magnetic Activity Levels, Metallicities, and Radii of Low-Mass Stars
| año = 2007
| publicación = [[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]]
| volumen = 660
| número = 1
| id = pp. 732-739
| url = http://cdsads.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?2007ApJ...660..732L&db_key=AST&nosetcookie=1
}}</ref>。它的[[恆星自轉|自轉速度]]小於2.8公里/秒，[[鐵|鐵]]的相對[[金屬量|豐度]]比太陽稍低<ref name=LopezMorales />。

已知[[飛馬座EQ|飛馬座EQ]]與葛利澤880相距只有3.96[[光年|光年]]，還有[[雙魚座BR|雙魚座BR]]和[[葛利澤829|葛利澤829]]分別是7.57光年和8.04光年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.stellar-database.com/Scripts/find_neighbors.exe?ID=157300&ly=15 |title=Stars within 15 light-years of Bonner Durchmusterung +15°4733 (The Internet Stellar Database) |access-date=2014-09-13 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924110203/http://www.stellar-database.com/Scripts/find_neighbors.exe?ID=157300&ly=15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。所有這些恆星都是紅矮星。

